# Nespresso mobile rows 1–11 FROZEN

Sam spent a full day tuning **sections / rows 1–11** and squiggles 1–11 in `mobile-case-nav.css`.

## Hard rule

- **NEVER edit** `mobile-case-nav.css` for rows 1–11, squiggles 1–11, or any `~ .timeline-item` stack rule.
- **NEVER** add `:not()` / remove / rewrite stack rules to fix row 12.
- **NEVER** “restore” section 6 (or any 1–10) from an old git commit.

## Row 12 only

All mega menu / row 12 work lives in **`web-main/css/nespresso-mobile-row-12.css`** (loaded after `mobile-case-nav.css` on `nespresso-page.html`).

- Use `!important` on row 12 `transform` so `~` stacks in `mobile-case-nav.css` cannot override.
- Move image + text together on `.timeline-item` — never flex `order` splits.

## Squiggle 12

Squiggle 12 tail position stays in `mobile-case-nav.css` only if Sam explicitly asks; default row 12 content tuning is `nespresso-mobile-row-12.css`.

## Required check

After any row 12 change: hard refresh, confirm rows 1–10 still match saved commit `6bf6e97` baseline in `mobile-case-nav.css`.
